# @COMMENT: This refers to an event apparently late in Muḥammad's life when it became difficult for him to complete the recitation of the prayer. It is not found in the redaction of Ibn Hishām, nor is the phrase "Umm al-Qur'an." This represents one of Ibn Isḥāq's most frequently reused passages. Placement is based on content dealing with prayer. The passage is also found in WSACD: HBHXV37P409A, HBHXV37P413A, DRQSV02P099C, BYTXV01P131D, BQSXV02P234C, BQQXV01P056C, TTXXV02P222C, KTHRV04P580A, and HJRTV06P424B; WASKA: TMSXV02P116B, TMBXV01P406B, HKSXV03P194A, BQQXV01P056C, HMMXV02P264A, HMBSV03P082A, HKMXV02P200D, TTXXV02P222C; WYSAU: KHZXV03P036D; WMSAH: HBHXV37P343A, HBHXV37P410A, DWNXV01P217B, KHMSV01P205C, BQMXV03P080B, BQQXV01P056C, HKMXV02P200C, TTXXV02P222C, ASHDV03P495A, HJRTV06P424B; WABAB: KHZXV03P036D, BNHXV05P156C, BQQXV01P056C, TTXXV02P222C; WISUL: KHZXV03P036D, BNHXV05P086B, DRQSV02P097A, BQQXV01P056C, BRWXV11P044A, WAKMW: JNSMV01P088G, BQRXV01P207A, BQSXV02P234A, BQQXV01P056A, BQQXV01P056C, TTXXV02P218A, HJRTV06P424B; WHAYA: HBHXV37P368A, KHZXV03P036D, HAMAV02P197B, DHRSV03P107A, THSMV01P215C, HKSXV03P190A, BNHXV05P095A, DRQSV02P099B, BYTXV01P131D, BQQXV01P056A, BQQXV01P056C, BRWXV11P044A, TTXXV02P222C, KTHRV04P579B, HJRTV06P424B; WMAAI: BKHJV01P061C and BQQXV01P056C; WAANH: BRWXV11P044C, BNHXV05P095A, BQQXV01P056C, BRWXV11P044A, TTXXV02P222C, HJRTV06P424B; WUMHA: DRQSV02P099A, BQQXV01P056C, HJRTV06P424B; WISUL: HJRTV06P424B; WYAHA: BQQXV01P056C; WHSDB: BQQXV01P056C; and without a witness: IHMAV02P271A and BQQXV01P064B. @EC_01/17/23@ @EC_01/02/24@

